<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM11.2">
<l>eḻiluṭaiya vammaṉaimīr eṉṉaraṅkat tiṉṉamutar</l>
<l>kuḻalaḻakar vāyaḻakar kaṇṇaḻakar koppūḻil</l>
<l>eḻukamalap pūvaḻaka remmāṉā reṉṉuṭaiya</l>
<l>kaḻalvaḷaiyait tāmuṅ kaḻalvaḷaiyē yākkiṉarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O beautiful mothers! My sweet Nectar from Raṅgam</l>
<l>Has beautiful locks, a beautiful mouth, beautiful eyes,</l>
<l>And is handsome [due to] the lotus flower that rises from the navel.</l>
<l>Our Lord has turned my kaḻal¬-bangles into bangles that slip off.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
